title: Emmanuel Macron
deleted: On November 20 2020, Macron published a tweet in which he mourned the death of the Patriarch of the Serbian Orthodox Church, [[Miroslav Gavrilović|Miroslav Gavrilovic]], a known denier of the Bosnian genocide, and supporter of convicted war criminals [[Ratko Mladić]] and [[Radovan Karadžić|Radovan Karadzic]].<ref>{{Cite web|title=https://twitter.com/emmanuelmacron/status/1329858232123265028|url=https://twitter.com/emmanuelmacron/status/1329858232123265028|access-date=2020-11-21|website=Twitter|language=en}}</ref>
